==English==
===Noun===
'''dowry''' (''plural:'' '''dowries''')

#[[property]] or [[payment]] brought by a [[wife]] or her family to a [[husband]] at the time of [[marriage]]. (In some cultures, it is the husband who pays the dowry to the wife’s family.)

